  </div>

  <div class="card" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <h3 style="font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 15px;">Parámetros de Audioguías</h3>
    <div style="padding: 15px; background-color: #f5f5f5; border-radius: 8px; line-height: 1.8;">
      <p style="color: #1a1a1a; margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Formatos disponibles:</strong> MP3, AAC, OGG</p>
